The paper deals with the Learning With Errors (LWE) problem and its applications to cryptography and lattices. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also introduces a new algorithm for solving LWE, which involves techniques from information theory (cs.IT), data structures (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these categories are also likely to be relevant.
